			<CASNumber>14807-96-6</CASNumber>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Talcum powder is produced from talc, a mineral composed mainly of magnesium, silicon, and oxygen. It is used industrially and in cosmetics for its ability to absorb moisture, reduce friction, and improve texture. Talcum powder has been associated with health concerns due to potential asbestos contamination, which can lead to serious diseases such as mesothelioma and ovarian cancer. Legal actions have been taken against companies for not disclosing the risks associated with asbestos in talcum powder.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">滑石粉是由滑石粉制成的，滑石粉是一种主要由镁、硅和氧组成的矿物质。它在工业和化妆品中使用，因为它能够吸收水分，减少摩擦，改善质地。滑石粉由于潜在的石棉污染而与健康问题有关，这可能导致严重的疾病，如间皮瘤和卵巢癌。已对不披露与滑石粉中的石棉有关的风险的公司采取法律行动。</common:generalComment>
